window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ethan and his companions are recovering from the Tomb of Pendragon, but a new adventure calls. They have found an ancient journal belonging to the legendary wizard, Merlin, and it has directions to the ancient city.</p> <p>But dangers lurk on the road to Camelot, and possibly in Camelot itself. Before they know it, Ethan and his friends are swept into an adventure that may unveil untold secrets - or release untold evil.</p> <p>Join Ethan and his friends as they embark on a quest to find the Ruins of Camelot!</p>"; 
